                        "AcquisitionStrategy": {
                            "val": "VC-25A AMP is accomplished by developmental integration of commercial off-the-shelf systems, hardware procurement and installation is accomplished to align with heavy maintenance depot schedules.  An Undefinitized Contract Action (UCA) was issued in Jun 12.  The UCA was definitized with a Cost Plus Incentive Fee (CPIF) type contract April 2014.  The CPIF contract covers the engineering RDT&E effort through Critical Design Review in FY15.  The remaining RDT&E effort including the first kit, install and flight test was awarded in FY15 and concludes in FY18 with delivery of the first aircraft."
                        },
